race.comment: TSUKINO (4) has a handy record over this seven-furlong journey with two wins and a second from just four attempts. Looms as the main danger. STRIKE THE HEART (5) gets the deadly Vandyke/Maloney combination and can improve sharply on recent efforts. Keep very safe. ECHO HUNTER (7) ran a better race last start to finish fourth over 1350m at Ipswich. In the mix with the 2kg claim. TECHNA (6) made progress finishing midfield last start at Ipswich on soft going when well in the market. Could add some value to betting. SHOW ME THE STARS (8) resumed over 1200m at this track last start and finished 1.5 lengths back in third. In the mix.
